Application Web - Scrapper - Web

How to run my program :

''' I'm running Ubuntu 14.03''

1.- Unzip the file 
2.- Go to terminal and search for the cnn directory and run this command 
    'scrapy crawl cnn -o news.csv -t csv'
    (this will generate the news.cvs file in the cnn directory)
3.- I created a virtual enviroment named : Project3
4.- I activate the virtual enviroment from command line source bin/activate
5.- Inside the virtual enviroment I installed flask 
    >$ pip install flask 
6.- Open the file viewer.py  and edit the path to CVS file with the
    headlines in variable :
    CSV_FILE_PATH ='news.csv' (write the whole path to the file)
7.- Run the aplication :  pyton viewer.py
8.- Open the browser at http://127.0.0.1:5000/
9.- the aplication should display the news headlines
